=== 質量和大小 ===
[[File:SolarSystem_OrdersOfMagnitude_Sun-Jupiter-Earth-Moon.jpg|thumb]]（×0.10045），但仍比地球大一個數量級（×10.9733），大紅斑大約有二到三個地球大（數量級相同）]]

木星的[[質量|質量]]是太陽系其他行星質量總和的2.5倍，由於它的質量是如此巨大，因此太陽系的[[質心|質心]]落在太陽的[[光球層|太陽表面]]之外，距離太陽中心1.068[[太陽半徑|太陽半徑]]。雖然木星的直徑是地球的11倍，體積是地球的1,321倍，但是它的密度很低，質量只是地球的318倍<ref name="fact">{{cite web|url = http://nssdc.gsfc.nasa.gov/planetary/factsheet/jupiterfact.html|title = Jupiter Fact Sheet|publisher = NASA|last = Williams|first = David R.|accessdate = 2007-08-08|date = 2004-11-16|archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/62D9vKbZz?url=http://nssdc.gsfc.nasa.gov/planetary/factsheet/jupiterfact.html|archive-date = 2011-10-05|dead-url = yes}}</ref><ref name="burgess">{{page needed|date=May 2015}} {{cite book
 |first=Eric|last=Burgess|date=1982
 |title=By Jupiter: Odysseys to a Giant
 |url=https://archive.org/details/byjupiterodyssey0000burg|publisher=Columbia University Press|location=New York
 |isbn=0-231-05176-X}}</ref>。木星的半徑是[[太陽半徑|太陽半徑]]的十分之一<ref name=shu82>{{cite book
|first=Frank H.|last=Shu|date=1982
|title=The physical universe: an introduction to astronomy
|url=https://archive.org/details/physicaluniverse00shuf_239|page=[https://archive.org/details/physicaluniverse00shuf_239/page/n442 426]|series=Series of books in astronomy
|edition=12th|publisher=University Science Books
|isbn=0-935702-05-9}}</ref>，質量是[[太陽質量|太陽質量]]的千分之一，所以兩者的密度是相近的<ref name=davis_turekian05>{{cite book
|author=Davis, Andrew M.
|author2=Turekian, Karl K.
|title=Meteorites, comets, and planets
|volume=1|series=Treatise on geochemistry
|publisher=Elsevier|date=2005|isbn=0-08-044720-1
|page=624}}</ref>。"[[木星質量|木星質量]]"（M<sub>J</sub>或M<sub>Jup</sub>）通常被做為描述其它天體，特別是[[太陽系外行星|系外行星]]和[[棕矮星|棕矮星]]的質量單位。例如系外行星[[HD_209458_b|HD 209458 b]]的質量是0.69M<sub>Jup</sub>，而[[仙女座κb|仙女座κb]]的質量是12.8M<sub>Jup</sub><ref>{{cite web|url=http://exoplanet.eu/|title=The Extrasolar Planets Encyclopedia: Interactive Catalogue|publisher=Paris Observatory|author=Jean Schneider|date=2009|accessdate=2015-07-03|archive-date=2015-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151225035816/http://www.exoplanet.eu/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

理論模型顯示如果木星的質量比現在更大，而不是僅有目前的質量，它將會繼續收縮<ref name=Seager2007>{{cite journal
 |last=Seager |first=S.
 |author2=Kuchner, M. |author3=Hier-Majumder, C. A. |author4= Militzer, B.
 |title=Mass-Radius Relationships for Solid Exoplanets
 |journal=The Astrophysical Journal
 |volume=669 |issue=2 |pages=1279–1297 |date=2007
 |doi=10.1086/521346
 |arxiv=0707.2895 |bibcode=2007ApJ...669.1279S}}</ref>。質量上的些許改變，不會讓木星的[[半徑|半徑]]有明顯的變化，大約要在500[[地球質量|地球質量]]（1.6M<sub>Jup</sub>）才會有明顯的改變<ref name=Seager2007/>。儘管隨著質量的增加，內部會因為壓力的增加而縮小體積。結果是，木星被認為已經幾乎達到了行星結構和演化史所能決定的最大半徑<ref name=HTUW>{{cite AV media | title=How the Universe Works 3 | volume=Jupiter: Destroyer or Savior? | date=2014 | publisher=Discovery Channel}}</ref>。隨著質量的增加，收縮的過程會繼續下去，直到達到可察覺的[[恆星形成|恆星形成]]質量，大約是50M<sub>Jup</sub>的高質量[[棕矮星|棕矮星]]<ref name="tristan286">{{cite journal
 |last         = Guillot
 |first        = Tristan
 |title        = Interiors of Giant Planets Inside and Outside the Solar System
 |journal      = Science
 |date         = 1999
 |volume       = 286
 |issue        = 5437
 |pages        = 72–77
