 |doi          = 10.1126/science.286.5437.72
 |pmid         = 10506563
 |bibcode      = 1999Sci...286...72G
 |archive-date = 2009-09-17
 |archive-url  = https://web.archive.org/web/20090917163936/http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/full/286/5437/72
 |dead-url     = no
}}</ref>。

然而，需要75倍的木星質量才能使氫穩定的融合成為一顆恆星。最小的[[紅矮星|紅矮星]]，半徑大約只是木星的30% <ref>{{cite journal
 |author = Burrows, A.
 |author2 = Hubbard, W. B.
 |author3 = Saumon, D.
 |author4 = Lunine, J. I.
 |title=An expanded set of brown dwarf and very low mass star models
 |journal=Astrophysical Journal|date=1993|volume=406
 |issue=1|pages=158–71
 |bibcode=1993ApJ...406..158B |doi = 10.1086/172427
}}
</ref><ref>{{cite news
