=== 太空探索與探測 ===
{{main|木星探測}}

自1973年以來，有數艘自動化的太空船拜訪過木星，最引人注目的是[[先鋒10號|先鋒10號]]太空船。它是第一艘足夠接近木星，並發送回有關這顆太陽系最大行星的屬性和現象的太空船<ref>[http://quest.nasa.gov/sso/cool/pioneer10/mission/ NASA – Pioneer 10 Mission Profile] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151106205010/http://quest.nasa.gov/sso/cool/pioneer10/mission/ |date=2015-11-06 }}. NASA. Retrieved on December 22, 2011.</ref><ref>[http://www.nasa.gov/centers/glenn/about/history/pioneer.html NASA – Glenn Research Center] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nasa.gov/centers/glenn/about/history/pioneer.html |date=20170713041117 }}. NASA. Retrieved on December 22, 2011.</ref>。飛往太陽系內其他行星的太空船完全依賴能量的價值，太空船速度的淨變化或[[ΔV|ΔV]]。從地球的[[低地球軌道|低地球軌道]]進入到木星的[[霍曼轉移軌道|霍曼轉移軌道]]只需要6.3Km/s的ΔV<ref>Fortescue, Peter W.; Stark, John and Swinerd, Graham ''Spacecraft systems engineering'', 3rd ed., John Wiley and Sons, 2003, ISBN 978-0-470-85102-9 p. 150.</ref>，這媲美於要進入低地球軌道的9.7Km/s的ΔV<ref>{{cite web|last=Hirata |first=Chris |url=http://www.pma.caltech.edu/~chirata/deltav.html |title=Delta-V in the Solar System |publisher=California Institute of Technology |accessdate=2006-11-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060715015836/http://www.pma.caltech.edu/~chirata/deltav.html |archivedate=2006-07-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。幸運的是，[[重力助推|重力助推]]可以用來減少抵達木星所需要的能量，然而，這也很明顯的需要較長的飛行時間<ref name="delta-v">{{cite web|last = Wong|first = Al|date = 1998-05-28|url = http://www2.jpl.nasa.gov/galileo/faqnav.html|title = Galileo FAQ: Navigation|publisher = NASA|accessdate = 2006-11-28|archive-date = 2008-05-26|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080526232404/http://www2.jpl.nasa.gov/galileo/faqnav.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

